body:
Hey guys,
so Ive been not playing minecraft basically at all...
This makes me very sad to say but, I have to stop. I have alot of sports and school to focus on, but thats not really why. Im just bored as heck even if play with good friends. I will still be on teamspeak(sometimes) and will continue to play on my team. I might check the fourms once in a while too.
Thank you so much for giving me a opportunity to be part of this amazing community, I wish Avicus the best of luck to gain players back.

I might get on to play Once in a while

Im sorry if I have ever been rude/annoying to you.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Some people Id like to thank (Everybody on teamspeak) (Ill keep it short)

Gummi3 - Fuck you ur bad
jk
Seriously, I dont know where to start, We have been friends for more than a year now and have so many messed up memories of us being retarded.  When I first met you you were a random that was trash at pvp, how times have changed :P I hope we can still play together as often as we usually do and I hope you get silver 1 one dayyyy.
----
BlamePotLag - Bad as well (not kidding either)
I remember when I met you and your 10 fps. You were still cocky if you lost and thats what I still love about you to this day.
You and Gummi3 are great friends and an "exciting" group to be with and I thank you.
----
ebirdy9 (YoUrFaCeHaHa)
We've definitly had some stupid fights, but I hope we can still be friends.
Thanks for introducing me to this great network.
----
lil_greg15
Ive known you since you first got on, always that weird ass laugh and a funny personality.
Keep that going greg.
-----
merlinmaster

Whooo!
Yeahhh!
Yeah. What's up?
Go Cory! (Go, go!)
Go Cory! (Go, go, go, go!)
Listen up
Here we go!



I'm the new kid, moving in
Getting it done
And I'm officially the candidate
For having some fun
You know

[Background Vocals: Maiana Walsh]

You better calm down Cory
(yea yea)



I'm talking 'bout an all-out party
And we're getting it started
Mr. President, you mind some electric guitar?



Washington D.C. will never be the same
Cause we've got



Cory, Cory, Cory
In the House (Yeah! It's a party every week, baby!)

Cory, Cory, Cory
Check it out (That's right, I'm in the House!)

He's gonna shake it up and change it (Shake it up)
Take it all and rearrange it (Just a little bit)
Got a new plan, hey Uncle Sam! (Look out now)
We've got Cory in the House! (Par-ty!)
Cory in the House! (I'm your man!)

cory’s burning down the white house with his dope ass bars.

-------

Fuseh

always a friend, and a rival <3

-------

bmb

one of the first people to try to teach me to pvp

ty

--------

smitdalt

no more of my nudes or ill hurt you

dy

------

storm997

i will never stop mi hax

-----

refuse

#RASE

-----

mooch24

how could I ever forget you, I looked up to you a ton!

Thanks for being a god mooch

-----

D00ZIE

Always nice to me <3

and always hard to beat :)

------

panda

comedy gold

------

broker

I still have your beatbox battle on my youtube channel

-----

Seth

i love you, dont say anymore...SHHHH

-----

Zaccc

Your a very funny and nice guy, thanks for letting me join your team

-----

DaBaderMc

even though me and you never really talk alot, we were always friends and you were always very respected by me

-----

Zeusy

razzledazzled

-----

ducksfanwaterlooloo

you were really funny, thanks

-----

steven

again, very funny.

I love your singing and your avicade skills

-----

dynamoh

still bad

I cant think of anyone right now, Im POSITIVE i missed a bunch of people so if your not listed, dont feel bad I forgot alot of people

anyone on teamspeak is my friend


--------------------------

Thank you kylo, for making this amazing server once again.





Well, I hope we can still continue to be friends on teamspeak or skype.

Now... I must go, I have pizza waiting in the microwave.

Thank You!

Goodbye, birdy.
